ng.Imaging>  \n Provides advanced [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](../../../../includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] imaging functionality.  \n  \n <xref:System.Drawing.Text>  \n Provides advanced [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](../../../../includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] typography functionality.  \n  \n <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>  \n Provides print-related services.  \n  \n <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TextRenderer>  \n Provides [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdi](../../../../includes/ndptecgdi-md.md)] text drawing and measuring functionality.","nodes":[{"pos":[12,62],"content":"Graphics Overview (Windows Forms) | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Graphics Overview (Windows Forms) | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,50]}]},{"pos":[549,582],"content":"Graphics Overview (Windows Forms)","linkify":"Graphics Overview (Windows Forms)","nodes":[{"content":"Graphics Overview (Windows Forms)","pos":[0,33]}]},{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">[!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](../../../../includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)]</ph> is a Graphics Device Interface that enables programmers to write device-independent applications.","pos":[583,748],"source":"[!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](../../../../includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] is a Graphics Device Interface that enables programmers to write device-independent applications."},{"content":"The services of <ph id=\"ph1\">[!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](../../../../includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)]</ph> are exposed through a set of managed classes.","pos":[749,878],"source":" The services of [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](../../../../includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] are exposed through a set of managed classes."},{"pos":[887,902],"content":"In This Section","linkify":"In This Section","nodes":[{"content":"In This Section","pos":[0,15]}]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Overview of Graphics<ept id=\"p1\">](../../../../docs/framework/winforms/advanced/overview-of-graphics.md)</ept>","pos":[906,998],"source":"[Overview of Graphics](../../../../docs/framework/winforms/advanced/overvi